<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EC) No 2234/98 of 16 October 1998 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 laying down detailed rules for the definition of lambs fattened as heavy carcases </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2234/98, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90, millega kehtestatakse rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatud tallede m&auml;&auml;ratlemise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad 16. oktoober 1998 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 of 25 September 1989 on the common organisation of the market in sheepmeat and goatmeat (1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1589/96 (2), and in particular Article 5(9) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 25. septembri 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 lamba- ja kitselihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1589/96, (2) eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 9, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 of 12 December 1989 defining lambs as heavy carcases (3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1266/95 (4), and in particular Article 1(2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 12. detsembri 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89, millega m&auml;&auml;ratletakse rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatud talled, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1266/95, (4) eriti selle artikli 1 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas detailed rules for definition of lambs fattened as heavy carcases were adopted by Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 (5), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1529/96 (6); </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumatud tallede m&auml;&auml;ratlemise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad on vastu v&otilde;etud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1529/96; (6) </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the second subparagraph of Article 1(1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 provides for the introduction of a simplified procedure for verification of fattening as heavy carcases with regard to lambs belonging to a limited number of meat breeds reared in geographically well-defined areas; whereas to that end Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 should be amended to simplify the administrative verification procedure laid down while maintaining the obligation on producers to fulfil the undertaking to actually fatten as heavy carcases all lambs born on their holdings; whereas that undertaking may be deemed to have been fulfilled where a check shows that the lambs present as a percentage of those which have been born is above a minimum threshold determined by reference to normal breeding practice for the breeds and areas concerned, and that the lambs have been kept for a period which allows them to fulfil the conditions on fattening laid down in Article 1(1) (c) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89; whereas control measures and penalties ensuing from the failure to fulfil the said undertaking should be foreseen; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 teises l&otilde;igus s&auml;testatakse lihtsustatud korra kehtestamine geograafiliselt selgepiirilistel aladel kasvatatud piiratud arvu lihat&otilde;ugudesse kuuluvate lammaste rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumamise kontrollimiseks; sel eesm&auml;rgil tuleks muuta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90, et lihtsustada etten&auml;htud halduskontrolli korda, s&auml;ilitades tootjate kohustuse k&otilde;ik oma talumajapidamistes s&uuml;ndinud talled tegelikult rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks nuumata; selle kohustuse v&otilde;ib lugeda t&auml;idetuks, kui kontrollimisel selgub, et olemasolevate tallede protsent s&uuml;ndinud tallede hulgas on suurem alamm&auml;&auml;rast, mis m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks asjakohaste t&otilde;ugude ja piirkondade harilike t&otilde;uaretustavade alusel, ja kui tallesid on hoitud talumajapidamistes piisavalt kaua, et talled vastaksid m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis c s&auml;testatud nuumamistingimustele; k&otilde;nealuse kohustuse t&auml;itmataj&auml;tmise eest tuleks ette n&auml;ha kontrollimeetmed ja karistused; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Sheep and Goats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las lamba- ja kitselihaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 of Regulation (EEC) No 2814/90 is replaced by the following text: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2814/90 artikkel 2 asendatakse j&auml;rgmisega: </eesti>
<inglise> 'Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> "Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Producers marketing sheep's milk or sheep's milk products who wish to benefit under the derogation provided for in the second subparagraph of Article 1(1) of Regulation (EEC) No 3901/89 with regard to lambs in the geographical areas and belonging to the breeds listed in the Annex hereto shall provide an undertaking, when making their premium application, to rear on the holding all lambs born to ewes declared in the application and to fatten them as heavy carcases. </inglise>
<eesti> Lambapiima v&otilde;i lambapiimatooteid turustavad tootjad, kes soovivad kasutada m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3901/89 artikli 1 l&otilde;ike 1 teises l&otilde;igus k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas loetletud geograafilistes piirkondades asuvate ja samas loetletud t&otilde;ugudesse kuuluvate tallede jaoks etten&auml;htud erandit, v&otilde;tavad endale lisatasu taotluse esitamise ajal kohustuse kasvatada oma p&otilde;llumajandusettev&otilde;ttes k&otilde;ik taotluses deklareeritud uttedele s&uuml;ndinud talled ja nuumata nad rasketeks r&uuml;mpadeks. </eesti>
<inglise> The undertaking shall be considered to have been fulfilled if, except in duly justified exceptional circumstances, the lambs on the holding are at least 70 % of the lambs that have been born and that they have been kept for a period of at least 75 days after birth. </inglise>
<eesti> Kohustus loetakse t&auml;idetuks, kui p&otilde;llumajandusettev&otilde;ttes olevad talled moodustavad 70% s&uuml;ndinud talledest ja kui neid on seal hoitud v&auml;hemalt 75 p&auml;eva p&auml;rast s&uuml;ndi, v&auml;lja arvatud n&otilde;uetekohaselt p&otilde;hjendatud erijuhtudel. </eesti>
<inglise> Producers fulfilling this undertaking shall receive the premium for the heavy category referred to in Article 5(4) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 in respect of all their eligible ewes. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;nealust kohustust t&auml;itvad tootjad saavad k&otilde;igi lisatasu saamise tingimustele vastavatele uttede eest m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud raske kategooria lisatasu. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Producers making this undertaking shall keep an up-to-date register, which shall include the movements of lambs (numbers of animals concerned by each entering or leaving operation) on at least the basis of aggregate movements stating as appropriate their origin or destination as well as the date of such movements and, in the case of the sale or slaughter of lambs, provide supporting documentation, such as sales notes or slaughter certificates. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootjad, kes v&otilde;tavad k&otilde;nealuse kohustuse, peavad ajakohastatud registrit, mis sisaldab andmeid tallede liikumise kohta ettev&otilde;ttesse (toodavate ja &auml;raviidavate loomade arv) v&auml;hemalt &uuml;ldise liikumise alusel ja m&auml;rgitakse vastavalt vajadusele loomade p&auml;ritolu v&otilde;i sihtkoht ja selliste liikumiste kuup&auml;ev ning tallede m&uuml;&uuml;gi v&otilde;i tapmise korral lisatakse t&auml;iendavad dokumendid, nagu m&uuml;&uuml;giteatised ja tapat&otilde;endid. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> Without prejudice to the requirements under the integrated system set down in Article 6(6) of Regulation (EEC) No 3887/92 the competent authority shall carry out an on-the-spot inspection at least once a year at the place of lambing of each of the producers submitting applications in respect of any marketing year. </inglise>
<eesti> Ilma et see piiraks m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3887/92 artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 6 s&auml;testatud &uuml;htse s&uuml;steemi n&otilde;uete kohaldamist, teeb p&auml;dev asutus v&auml;hemalt kord aastas kohapealseid kontrolle vastaval majandusaastal taotluse esitanud tootjaettev&otilde;tete lammaste poegimiskohtades. </eesti>
<inglise> Such inspections shall include a check of the lambs present on the holding and of those entered in the register kept by the producer together with supporting documentation, in order to determine whether the undertaking has been fulfilled. </inglise>
<eesti> Selleks kontrollitakse ettev&otilde;ttes olevate ja tootjate poolt registrisse kantud tallesid ja t&auml;iendavaid dokumente, et teha kindlaks, kas kohustus on t&auml;idetud. </eesti>
<inglise> In cases where the undertaking has not been fulfilled, only the premium for the light category may be paid for the eligible ewes. </inglise>
<eesti> Kohustuse t&auml;itmataj&auml;tmise korral v&otilde;ib lisatasu saamise tingimustele vastavate uttede puhul maksta &uuml;ksnes kerge kategooria lisatasu. </eesti>
<inglise> However, where the competent authority finds that the failure to comply with the undertaking is a result of a false notification made deliberately or through serious negligence, the producer concerned shall also lose the right to the premium in accordance with Article 5(3) of Regulation (EEC) No 3013/89 for the marketing year in respect of which the undertaking applies. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui p&auml;dev asutus leiab, et kohustuse t&auml;itmataj&auml;tmise p&otilde;hjuseks on tahtlikult v&otilde;i t&otilde;sise hooletuse t&otilde;ttu esitatud valeandmed, kaotab asjaomane tootja vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3013/89 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikele 3 &otilde;iguse lisatasule selle majandusaasta eest, mida kohustus h&otilde;lmas." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub j&auml;rgmisel p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall apply to applications for premiums presented for the 1999 marketing year and subsequent years. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolevat m&auml;&auml;rust kohaldatakse 1999. majandusaastaks ja j&auml;rgmisteks aastateks esitatud lisatasutaotluste suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 16 October 1998. </inglise>
